#: ../../developer-guide/release-process/index.en.rst:83
msgid ""
"These steps will create the distribution files and sign them using your "
"key. Expect to be prompted twice for your passphrase unless you use an "
"ssh key agent. If you have multiple keys you will need to set the default"
" appropriately beforehand, as no option will be provided to select the "
"signing key. The files should have names that start with "
"``trafficserver-X.Y.Z-rcA.tar.bz2`` where ``X.Y.Z`` is the version and "
"``A`` is the release candidate counter. There should be four such files, "
"one with no extension and three others with the extensions ``asc``, "
"``md5``, and ``sha1``. This will also create a signed git tag of the form"
" ``X.Y.Z-rcA``."
