msgid ""
"Send the release candiate announcement to the *users* and *dev* "
"mailinging lists, noting that it is a release *candidate* and providing a"
" link to the distribution files you uploaded. This announcement should "
"also call for a vote on the candidate, generally with a 72 hours time "
"limit."
